million shares traded, industrial 127.128 million, construction
57.571 million, trade/services 251.358 million, infrastructure
3.261 million, finance 176.617 million, hotel 12.241 million,
properties 411.046 million, plantation 56.116 million, mining
9.271 million, trusts 1,155 million, loan stocks 255.487 million,
call warrants 6.221 million and main board rights 721,462.
