<P>
The second board turnover rose to 314.830 million shares worth
4.195 billion ringgit (about 1.678 billion dollars) from 242.102
million shares valued at 3.005 billion ringgit (about 1.202
billion dollars) last week.
</P>
<P>
Off market deals amounted 185.347 million shares worth 1.504
billion ringgit (about 601.6 million dollars) against 380.540
million shares worth 2.191 billion ringgit (about 876.4 million
dollars) last week. 
</P>
