<TEXT>
<P>
MONTEVIDEO, January 24 (Xinhua) -- Nine corporate groups have
showed interest in bidding for the bridge project that will
connect Buenos Aires, the Argentine capital, with the city of
Colonia in the east of Uruguay.
</P>
<P>
The Montevideo-based binational commission in charge of the
project said it had sold four sets of the specifications to the
nine groups who were to participate in the bidding.
</P>
