<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, January 24 (Xinhua) -- A Colombian minister today
labelled as "unjust" the statement of the U.S. Secretary of State,
who said Thursday in a letter to U.S. Congress that Mexico and
Colombia's struggles against drug trafficking were inadequate.
</P>
