this issue be resolved in the interest of Russia and NATO.
</P>
<P>
Talbott said that the enlargement of NATO is an important and
complicated issue, but the two sides will find a solution.
</P>
<P>
Talbott arrived in Moscow Wednesday for the preparation of the
meeting between Chernomyrdin and Gore and he is expected to leave
for home today. 
